# Google Tag Manager container ID — this is the ONLY value the app needs.
# Everything else (which SDK to load, the Rebrandly API key, the API base URL,
# the conversion tags) is configured INSIDE the GTM container — see /setup.
#
# Use your own GTM container so you can edit tags/triggers and use Preview mode.
VITE_GTM_ID=GTM-XXXXXXX
